original_font_information.trademark: Brush Script is a Trademark of Monotype Typography ltd.
original_font_information.description: This heavy, informal script looks as though it was written with a brush because its lowercase letters join together. Use the uppercase letters primarily as initials, although you might find it interesting to use all capitals of this typeface for some words.
